        <updateDate>2020-07-30T16:34:23Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Flint Registry Reauthorization Act</b></p> <p>This bill extends through FY2031 a voluntary lead exposure registry supported by the Centers for Disease Control and Prevention. The registry collects data on the exposure of individuals in Flint, Michigan, to lead contamination in the local drinking water system.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
